A.aUD=new B.Z(A.ME,["Regi\xf3n: {region}","Tema: {topic}","\u03c9: {value}","\u03c3: {value}","I\u03c4: {value}","J\u03bc: {value}","\u03c3: observado {scs}/100","I\u03c4: observado {scs}/100","J\u03bc: observado {scs}/100","EL CONTINUUM: {lean} ({reg}% regresivo / {prog}% progresivo)","El escenario se lee {lean} ({reg}% regresivo / {prog}% progresivo) \u2014 las recomendaciones reducen la probabilidad del escenario y reparan la cohesi\xf3n; no amplificar el momento regresivo.","El escenario se lee {lean} ({reg}% regresivo / {prog}% progresivo) \u2014 las recomendaciones sostienen la cohesi\xf3n progresiva.","Objetivo: reducir la probabilidad de {subject}, no amplificar el momento REGRESIVO.","Objetivo: sostener la cohesi\xf3n PROGRESIVA en {subject}.","(mitigaci\xf3n \u2014 reducir probabilidad del escenario)","(apoyo \u2014 sostener cohesi\xf3n progresiva)","PARTE TRES \u2014 Acciones de mitigaci\xf3n para el/la {agent} (inclinaci\xf3n REGRESIVA)","PARTE TRES \u2014 Acciones de apoyo para el/la {agent} (inclinaci\xf3n PROGRESIVA)","PARTE TRES \u2014 Reparaci\xf3n de cohesi\xf3n para el/la {agent} (inclinaci\xf3n REGRESIVA)","PARTE TRES \u2014 Sostenimiento de cohesi\xf3n para el/la {agent} (inclinaci\xf3n PROGRESIVA)",'Objetivo de mitigaci\xf3n: ~{current}% \u2192 ~{projected}% en "{subject}" (reducir, no elevar)','Objetivo de apoyo: ~{current}% \u2192 ~{projected}% en "{subject}"','Reparaci\xf3n de cohesi\xf3n: SCS ~{current} \u2192 {min}\u2013{max} en "{subject}" (contrarrestar inclinaci\xf3n REGRESIVA)','Sostenimiento de cohesi\xf3n: SCS ~{current} \u2192 {min}\u2013{max} en "{subject}"','Estos pasos pueden reducir la estimaci\xf3n de "{subject}" de ~{current}% hacia ~{projected}% \u2014 mitigaci\xf3n, no amplificaci\xf3n.','Estos pasos pueden elevar la estimaci\xf3n constructiva de "{subject}" de ~{current}% hacia ~{projected}%.',"Estos pasos pueden elevar la cohesi\xf3n de ~{current}/100 hacia {min}\u2013{max}/100 para contrarrestar el momento REGRESIVO.","Estos pasos pueden sostener la cohesi\xf3n de ~{current}/100 hacia {min}\u2013{max}/100 en 3 meses.","V\xf3rtice","Cizalla","Resistencia","Flujo","Continuum","Variable \u03c9 de circulaci\xf3n relativa a su pregunta planteada \u2014 encuadre de \xe9lite, compresi\xf3n de autoridad\u2026","Sesgo \u2014 encuadre polarizado, queja, percepci\xf3n de dos niveles\u2026","Sesgo opuesto \u2014 inercia institucional, escepticismo\u2026","Matices \u2014 transporte de confianza, continuidad covariante\u2026",u.R,"{n} {label}","Grok","@grok \xb7 respuesta observacional Chronoflux","Respuesta @grok copiada","Informe copiado","PLANTEE SU PREGUNTA EN EL V\xd3RTICE CHRONOFLUX","Escriba cualquier pregunta \u03c9 o escenario mundial en el campo V\xf3rtice (\u03c9) abajo.","Rellene V\xf3rtice (\u03c9), Cizalla (\u03c3), Resistencia (I\u03c4) y Flujo (J\u03bc) \u2014 o active Grok construal.","Grok construal rellena \u03c9/\u03c3/I\u03c4/J\u03bc desde su pregunta. Edite cualquier campo para anular.","Pulse Calcular probabilidad para su estimaci\xf3n Chronoflux.","PEGUE UN ENLACE \u2014 LE DIR\xc9 LA PUNTUACI\xd3N DE COHESI\xd3N SOCIAL DE ESTA NARRATIVA","Pegue la URL de un art\xedculo, declaraci\xf3n o narrativa en el campo de enlace abajo.","Pulse Leer narrativa del enlace \u2014 Evolve extrae el texto de la p\xe1gina al V\xf3rtice (\u03c9).","Rellene \u03c9/\u03c3/I\u03c4/J\u03bc manualmente o active Grok construal, luego calcule la cohesi\xf3n social.","Grok construal rellena \u03c9/\u03c3/I\u03c4/J\u03bc desde la narrativa cargada. Revise y calcule.","URL de la narrativa","https://ejemplo.com/articulo\u2026","Leer narrativa del enlace","Leyendo narrativa del enlace\u2026","Narrativa cargada \u2014 rellenando \u03c9/\u03c3/I\u03c4/J\u03bc desde el enlace.","Introduzca un enlace http o https v\xe1lido.","No se pudo leer el enlace. Compruebe la URL, pruebe https://, o pegue el texto en su pregunta planteada.","La p\xe1gina devolvi\xf3 poco o ning\xfan texto legible (muro de acceso o solo JavaScript). Pegue el art\xedculo en su pregunta planteada.","El sitio bloque\xf3 la lectura autom\xe1tica (com\xfan en X, Facebook, Instagram, TikTok y otras redes). Use Evolve en escritorio con el proxy Grok, o pegue la narrativa en su pregunta planteada.","Inicie sesi\xf3n con X (barra Grok construal) para leer publicaciones de X/Twitter y vuelva a intentar el enlace.","Narrativa cargada. Inicie sesi\xf3n con X para completar \u03c9/\u03c3/I\u03c4/J\u03bc desde el texto y calcule."],t.w)
A.aUE=new B.Z(A.ME,["Region: {region}","Topic: {topic}","\u03c9: {value}","\u03c3: {value}","I\u03c4: {value}","J\u03bc: {value}","\u03c3: observed {scs}/100","I\u03c4: observed {scs}/100","J\u03bc: observed {scs}/100","THE CONTINUUM: {lean} ({reg}% regressive / {prog}% progressive)","Scenario reads {lean} ({reg}% regressive / {prog}% progressive) \u2014 recommendations reduce scenario likelihood and repair cohesion; do not amplify regressive momentum.","Scenario reads {lean} ({reg}% regressive / {prog}% progressive) \u2014 recommendations sustain progressive cohesion.","Aim: reduce likelihood of {subject}, not amplify REGRESSIVE momentum.","Aim: sustain PROGRESSIVE cohesion on {subject}.","(mitigation \u2014 reduce scenario likelihood)","(support \u2014 sustain progressive cohesion)","PART THREE \u2014 Mitigation actions for the {agent} (REGRESSIVE lean)","PART THREE \u2014 Support actions for the {agent} (PROGRESSIVE lean)","PART THREE \u2014 Cohesion repair for the {agent} (REGRESSIVE lean)","PART THREE \u2014 Cohesion sustainment for the {agent} (PROGRESSIVE lean)",'Mitigation target: ~{current}% \u2192 ~{projected}% on "{subject}" (reduce, not raise)','Support target: ~{current}% \u2192 ~{projected}% on "{subject}"','Cohesion repair: SCS ~{current} \u2192 {min}\u2013{max} on "{subject}" (counter REGRESSIVE lean)','Cohesion sustainment: SCS ~{current} \u2192 {min}\u2013{max} on "{subject}"','These steps may lower the estimate for "{subject}" from ~{current}% toward ~{projected}% \u2014 mitigation, not amplification.','These steps may raise the constructive estimate for "{subject}" from ~{current}% toward ~{projected}%.',"These steps may raise cohesion from ~{current}/100 toward {min}\u2013{max}/100 to counter REGRESSIVE momentum.","These steps may sustain cohesion from ~{current}/100 toward {min}\u2013{max}/100 within 3 months.","Vortex","Shear","Resistance","Flow","Continuum","\u03c9 circulation variable relative to your posed question \u2014 elite framing, authority compression\u2026",u.H,u.h,u.l,"Baseline \u2192 refined: {from} \u2192 {to} (\u0394 {delta})","{n} {label}","Grok","@grok \xb7 Chronoflux observational reply","Copied @grok reply","Report copied","POSE YOUR SCENARIO QUESTION \u2014 THEN ADD \u03c9/\u03c3/I\u03c4/J\u03bc VARIABLES","Type your base question in POSE YOUR QUESTION HERE \u2014 this anchors every calculation.","Fill Vortex (\u03c9), Shear (\u03c3), Resistance (I\u03c4), and Flow (J\u03bc) \u2014 or turn on Grok construal to auto-fill them.","Grok construal fills \u03c9/\u03c3/I\u03c4/J\u03bc from your question as you type. Edit any field to override.","Tap Calculate percent chance for your Chronoflux probability.","PASTE A LINK \u2014 I'LL LET YOU KNOW THE SOCIAL COHESION SCORE OF THIS NARRATIVE","Paste a news article, statement, or narrative URL in the link field below.","Tap Read narrative from link \u2014 Evolve loads the page text into POSE YOUR QUESTION HERE.","Fill \u03c9/\u03c3/I\u03c4/J\u03bc manually, or turn on Grok construal, then Calculate social cohesion score.","Grok construal fills \u03c9/\u03c3/I\u03c4/J\u03bc from the loaded narrative. Review, then Calculate social cohesion score.","Narrative URL","https://example.com/article\u2026","Read narrative from link","Reading narrative from link\u2026","Narrative loaded \u2014 \u03c9/\u03c3/I\u03c4/J\u03bc fields are being filled from the link text.","Enter a valid http or https link.","Could not read that link. Check the URL, try https://, or paste the narrative text into your posed question manually.","That page returned little or no readable text (often a login wall or JavaScript-only layout). Paste the article text into your posed question manually.","That site blocked automated reading (common on X, Facebook, Instagram, TikTok, and other social links). Run Evolve desktop with the Grok proxy, or paste the narrative text into your posed question manually.","Sign in with X (Grok construal bar) to read posts from X/Twitter, then try the link again.","Narrative loaded. Sign in with X to fill \u03c9/\u03c3/I\u03c4/J\u03bc from the text, then calculate."],t.w)
